FBIS4-35906 "drnes107_l_94009" FBIS-NES-94-107 Daily Report 3 Jun 1994 ISRAEL Parts of Negev, Galilee Declared Drought Areas Parts of Negev, Galilee Declared Drought Areas TA0306105994 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0700 GMT 3 Jun 94 TA0306105994 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Hebrew BFN [Text] The finance and agriculture ministers have declared parts of the Negev and the Galilee as drought areas. Our correspondent Shulamit Schmerling reports that as a result of the decision, farmers will be eligible for compensation. The Agriculture Ministry estimates that the scope of damages will reach a total of 10 million shekels.
